{"type":"message","id":"9d530ff5","parentId":"f0761b95","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:21:41.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly. Let me analyze the current situation:\n\n1. Current time: 3:12 AM UTC (April 7, 2026) which is 8:42 AM IST (UTC+5:30)\n2. This is within active hours (7 AM - 11 PM IST)\n3. I need to check all heartbeat tasks:\n\n**Time check first:** Get current IST time - 8:42 AM IST ✓\n\n**Inactive hours:** Not in inactive hours (11 PM - 7 AM IST) so proceed with checks\n\n**Pending tasks:** I searched for \"pending\" and found no current pending tasks mentioned by Nemesis in recent chats. The pending tasks found were historical/resolved.\n\n**Group vibes:** Check if it's been 3+ hours since last group message. Let me check GROUP.md for timestamp... Actually, I need to check when the last group message was. Looking at GROUP.md, I don't see explicit timestamps. Let me check memory files for recent group activity.\n\nActually, looking at the heartbeat health alert earlier, it showed:\n- groupmessage: CRITICAL - 1066 min since last run (threshold: 360 min)\nThat's over 17 hours since last group message check/run.\n\nBut according to HEARTBEAT.md: \"Check if it's been 3+ hours since the last group message (-1003606834639). ONLY send a message if you have something highly relevant or valuable to share based on recent context.\"\n\nI need to check if there's been 3+ hours since the last GROUP message (not since I last checked). Let me look for recent group messages in memory.\n\nActually, let me approach this systematically by checking what HEARTBEAT.md requires:\n\n1. **Time check first:** Done - IST is 8:42 AM\n2. **Inactive hours:** Not inactive (8:42 AM IST is between 7 AM - 11 PM IST)\n3. **Pending tasks:** No pending tasks found from Nemesis in recent context\n4. **Group vibes:** Check if 3+ hours since last group message\n5. **Group supervision:** Read last 10 group messages