e Persistence (MANDATORY - Last Step):** After completing all checks above, ALWAYS persist state to `memory/heartbeat-state.json`.\n\nNow I need to check each item:\n\nFirst, check pending tasks - search memory for any pending tasks mentioned by Nemesis.\n\nThen check group vibes - need to know when last group message was.\n\nThen group supervision - read last 10 group messages.\n\nThen ping Nemesis - check last DM time.\n\nThen group memory - check if significant group activity.\n\nLet me start by checking memory for pending tasks.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-b565d24855f0fa47","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"pending task Nemesis mentioned","maxResults":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":42020,"output":1244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775541181856,"responseId":"gen-1775541182-xng0kG63ENZKZmP5pTLx"}}
