ntion and no alerts are needed. According to Exit Protocol: \"If no tasks require attention and no alerts are needed, send absolutely NOTHING. Execute a silent exit.\"\n\nI should also update the heartbeat state as the final step.\n\nLet me update the heartbeat state and then send nothing.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-a77c0e5d95b27315","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 ./skills/heartbeat-state-manager/scripts/update_state.py --field heartbeat_run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":48415,"output":2167,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775543268742,"responseId":"gen-1775543269-1AqdNYrChrGwNTEl6kLN"}}
