ping him about unless he asked for it.\n\nActually, let me check if Nemesis mentioned anything about wanting war updates or if there's something specific.\n\nFrom memory search, I don't see any specific request for war updates from Nemesis.\n\nSo based on all checks:\n- Time check: done (12:04 PM IST)\n- Inactive hours: not inactive (active hours 7 AM-11 PM IST)\n- Pending tasks: no specific pending tasks from Nemesis found\n- Group vibes: less than 3 hours since last group message, so no group message needed\n- Group supervision: checked recent context, no indication I said anything wrong in group that needs correction\n- Ping Nemesis: less than 4 hours since last DM, and no relevant alert/pending task to ping about\n- Group memory: group_message task already ran recently (04:40 UTC), so GROUP.md should be updated\n\nTherefore, no tasks require attention and no alerts are needed. According to HEARTBEAT.md Exit Protocol: \"If no tasks require attention and no alerts are needed, send absolutely NOTHING. Execute a silent exit.\"\n\nBut I also need to do State Persistence: \"After completing all checks above, ALWAYS persist state to memory/heartbeat-state.json\"\n\nI've been doing that periodically, but I should do it one final time.\n\nLet me update the heartbeat state one more time and then exit silently.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-978f13aa347452fe","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 ./skills/heartbeat-state-manager/scripts/update_state.py --field heartbeat_run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":49220,"output":2626,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51846,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775543666054,"responseId":"gen-1775543667-J0J6Pb7ioRSzu99Tf1Tg"}}
