ly via group_message task\n\nTherefore, no tasks require attention and no alerts are needed. According to Exit Protocol, I should send absolutely NOTHING and execute a silent exit.\n\nHowever, I need to persist state to memory/heartbeat-state.json as the last step. I'll update the heartbeat_run field.\n\nLet me do that now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-be835eb210f08a33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 ./skills/heartbeat-state-manager/scripts/update_state.py --field heartbeat_run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":49317,"output":2163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51480,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775543727457,"responseId":"gen-1775543728-pT04NXNLr1yun9FiBJLC"}}
